Highlights:

* Implement an evolutionary algorithm to prove hidden relationship between a given predicate and a given concept (#1055, #1072, #1078, #1079, #1085, #1086, #1097, #1117, #1118)
* Implemented nested CHAIN operator for MeTTa queries (#1080)
* Database Adapter multiple threads (#1070)
* Refactor Database Adapter (#1105, #1106, #1113)
* Implement atom_count() and empty() in AtomDB (#1095)
* New QueryAnswer, AB flags and chain logic (#1096)
* Transforming the Database Adapter into an AtomDB (#1091)
* Add optional parameter to make AND operator consider last clause as a NOT (#1103)
* Implement ANDNOT operator in Pattern Matching query engine (#1104)
* Implementation of MorkDB Adapter (#1110, #1119, #1124, #1128)
* Method to recursively get all terminals reachable from a given handle (#1108)

Minor Changes:
* Remove unused AtomDBCache (#1068)
* [AtomDB] Remove ENV VARS (#1071)
* Add regression test for AdapterDB (#1116)

